00:23:36.416 --> 00:23:39.586 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR] Shido has succeeded
in opening Mukuro's heart.

00:23:39.669 --> 00:23:41.254 position:50% align:center
And as a new battle begins,

00:23:41.338 --> 00:23:44.090 position:50% align:center
a brand-new Origami and
Tohka come to life.

00:23:44.174 --> 00:23:46.843 position:50% align:center
Next time: "Locked Memories."

00:23:46.926 --> 00:23:49.888 position:50% align:center
[MUKURO]
Be tasty! Moe Moe Kyun!